xt on a black background, or “dark mode,” makes the eye work harder and open wider, since it needs to absorb more light. When this happens, the white letters can bleed into the black background and cause the text to blur, which is also known as the “halation” effect.\r\n\r\n供大家参考。", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://rxoptical.com/eye-health/is-dark-mode-better-for-your-eyes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://rxoptical.com/eye-health/is-dark-mode-better-for-your-eyes/</a></p>\n<p>其中有这样的一段话：</p>\n<p>White text on a black background, or “dark mode,” makes the eye work harder and open wider, since it needs to absorb more light. When this happens, the white letters can bleed into the black background and cause the text to blur, which is also known as the “halation” effect.</p>\n<p>供大家参考。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1622708804, "replies": 62, "id": 781158}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_large.png?m=1616560364", "name": "reading", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_normal.png?m=1616560364", "title": "阅读", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/reading", "topics": 462, "footer": "", "header": "少上网，多读书", "title_alternative": "Reading", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_mini.png?m=1616560364", "stars": 1208, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 111, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"username": "meetocean", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/00d9/139c/222331_mini.png?m=1492393888", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/meetocean", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1490150694, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/00d9/139c/222331_mini.png?m=1492393888", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/00d9/139c/222331_mini.png?m=1492393888", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 222331}, "last_reply_by": "meetocean", "last_touched": 1622790861, "title": "发了一本新书叫幻景时空，需要网友的建议", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/781173", "